messages.content: Good. I got one more year of school. Have fun in Seattle. I'll let you know if I'm in DC another time
Oh that's cool. Visiting cousins and finding work. How's the teaching certificate process going?
I wasn't in Laura this last year. I've been trying to get a teaching certificate in the states. I'm in Indiana now. What are doing in Seattle?
DC's lit btw, if you do go
But damn how you been man?
And I already came to Seattle for the summer. I'll be back in DC around August if you're still able to pull through.
Dude when did you leave majol?

Hi Patsy. Are you staying in DC this summer? I'll be in DC next weekend, and I'm curious to hear how you like it there. I'll buy you lunch somewhere, if you have time to kill. If not, no problem. Hope you're doing well
